arts.ttl: Vincenzo Grifo salvages point late on for Freiburg against Eintracht Frankfurt
arts.sum: Freiburg come from behind to draw 2-2 at home to Eintracht Frankfurt with Vincenzo Grifo's superb long-range free-kick cancelling out Jonathan Burkardt's first-half brace, which had overturned Derry Scherhant's early opener. It took Scherhant just two minutes to fire home the opening goal on his first Bundesliga start for Freiburg.

arts.ttl: Freiburg vs. Eintracht Frankfurt preview: Schuster's side eye unbeaten streak extension
arts.sum: Europa Park-Stadion hosts an intriguing Bundesliga clash on Sunday afternoon as Freiburg look to extend their unbeaten run against an Eintracht Frankfurt side looking to rediscover their rythym.
